(17, 6, NULL, 'Need to make changes to the Lead Tracking Report and Lead Create Form, and arrange the menus properly', '2026-05-18', '2026-05-18', 'Medium', 'Completed', 12, 8, '<p>Add Referred By in Lead Tracking. Hide the Referred By field in the Create Lead Form if the user already exists<br>Need to arrange the menus properly<br><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">order filter is not working properly</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\"><br></span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">&nbsp;hide option for exiting user of refer_by In lead create</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">add option lead tracking report add refer user in this anyone create lead and add refer show in this user&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">default data show after 15 may in trakicng report</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">order filter and lead filter after refresh show filter data whenever reset on click&nbsp;</span></li></ol><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\"><br></span><b style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">New Chages</b></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">1.&nbsp; When CLick On deadline change opition to feedback date to deadline and it change only admin</b></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">2.&nbsp; when select feedback status show option of feedback date and as well as in edit (order edit)</b></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\"><br></b></p><h3><h1></h1></h3>', NULL, '2026-05-20 07:43:32', '2026-05-26 04:42:28', '2026-05-26 04:42:28'),
