(110, 6, NULL, 'Changes by sir', '2026-05-21', '2026-05-21', 'Hard', 'Completed', 12, 8, '<li data-section-id=\"1x8ldhj\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"85\">Displayed the last lead status before conversion under the order status section.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1jnj4a8\" data-start=\"87\" data-end=\"169\">\r\nAdded writer status date display below the writer deadline in the order view.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"vnxvlq\" data-start=\"171\" data-end=\"273\">\r\nRestricted ticket generation for Dissertation orders even after feedback status is updated twice.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1xda5n5\" data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"403\">\r\nAdded an <strong data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"292\">R</strong> button in the order action section for refund requests and displayed the refund indicator in the order view.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1vm6wzk\" data-start=\"405\" data-end=\"513\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nAdded total order count beside the username in leads and included the latest comment column in the table</li><li data-section-id=\"1vm6wzk\" data-start=\"405\" data-end=\"513\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Added a new <strong data-start=\"15\" data-end=\"20\">A</strong> button. On click, a modal should open with two input fields: <strong data-start=\"82\" data-end=\"107\">Additional Word Count</strong> and <strong data-start=\"112\" data-end=\"132\">Additional Price</strong>.</li><li data-section-id=\"1vm6wzk\" data-start=\"405\" data-end=\"513\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Displayed the additional word count in the writer field and the additional price in the price field on the order list page.</li>', NULL, '2026-05-22 04:57:04', '2026-05-22 11:15:00', '2026-05-22 11:15:00'),
