(280, NULL, NULL, 'AIN Changes', '2026-05-27', '2026-05-27', 'Medium', 'Completed', 12, 8, '<li data-section-id=\"o28idp\" data-start=\"79\" data-end=\"130\">Fixed blog content formatting issues on frontend.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"178hj2m\" data-start=\"131\" data-end=\"221\">\r\nCleaned unwanted span, inline styles, and mismatched heading styles from blog content.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1qjc35q\" data-start=\"222\" data-end=\"288\">\r\nMade Add Blog and Edit Blog Summernote editor format consistent.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"19nhjx1\" data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"365\">\r\nFixed Summernote loading issue and resolved editor height/display problem.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1xaqqwp\" data-start=\"366\" data-end=\"434\">\r\nImproved blog content UI for headings, paragraphs, and list items.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1052edu\" data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"492\">\r\nAdded CSS fixes for ul, ol, and li bullet points.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1sjv6t\" data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"570\">\r\nMade the right-side form and WhatsApp image sticky on the blog detail page.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"i9hmoo\" data-start=\"17\" data-end=\"116\">Updated the <strong data-start=\"31\" data-end=\"56\">User Retention Report</strong> logic to show month-wise data only up to the current month.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1telwxv\" data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"216\">\r\nChanged the retention logic to check users based on future orders instead of past order history.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1222c2c\" data-start=\"218\" data-end=\"307\">\r\nFixed the <strong data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"250\">Not Retain Users</strong> list by excluding users whose last order date is null.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"15m6jsb\" data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"412\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nAdded proper month limit so future months like June onward do not show when the current month is May.</li><li data-section-id=\"1bmj7fb\" data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"697\">\r\nAdded author name display on blog detail page using author id from the blog table and author data from the author table.</li><li data-section-id=\"1bmj7fb\" data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"697\"><br><span style=\"font-size: 0.84rem;\">PrimeAssignment</span>&nbsp;<br></li><li data-section-id=\"rjyros\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"94\">Worked on the PrimeAssignment WordPress website built with the Seoes Marketing Agency theme.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1luz5m2\" data-start=\"95\" data-end=\"134\">\r\nReviewed blog content styling issues.</li><li data-section-id=\"1luz5m2\" data-start=\"95\" data-end=\"134\">Added responsive CSS improvements for better mobile view.</li>', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:48:09', '2026-05-29 12:49:03', '2026-05-29 12:49:03'),
