(298, 15, NULL, 'Home Page fully redesgin and fully responsive and also work on country page', '2026-05-29', '2026-05-29', 'Medium', 'Completed', 28, 24, '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"e1730259-52c4-4a39-ae2b-28f376c62e41\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1\" data-turn-start-message=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden\"><div class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling\"><ul data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"555\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-is-last-node=\"\"><li data-section-id=\"1ga707\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"180\">Redesigned the complete Home Page with a modern and user-friendly UI structure, improving overall layout, section alignment, and visual presentation for a better user experience.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"y90y43\" data-start=\"182\" data-end=\"363\">\r\nImplemented full responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices, ensuring proper spacing, smooth section adjustments, and optimized performance across all screen sizes.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"7xpjkf\" data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"555\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nWorked on Country Pages by improving page structure, dynamic content handling, responsiveness, and UI consistency to maintain a clean and seamless experience across all country-wise pages.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start\"></div><div class=\"mt-3 w-full empty:hidden\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl\"><div class=\"bg-token-main-surface-tertiary w-px flex-1 self-stretch\"></div></div></div></div>', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:22:2