(49, 19, 'Early Leave', 'Gatepass Leave', '1026-05-23', '1026-05-23', NULL, NULL, 'Due to personal reason', 'Dear Sir/Madam,\n\nI hope you are doing well.\n\nI would like to request an early leave for today, 23 May 2026, due to a personal reason that requires my attention. I kindly request you to grant me permission to leave early today.\n\nThank you for your understanding and consideration.\n\nSincerely,\n\nYashpal Singh\nSEO Executive', 'approved', 0.125, '2026-05-23 04:20:24', '2026-05-26 07:47:00'),
