(51, 19, 'Full Day', 'Casual Leave', '2026-05-29', '2026-05-30', NULL, NULL, 'family function', 'Dear: sir/mam\nI hope you are doing well.\nI would like to formally request leave for the 29th and 30th of May due to a family function.\nI will ensure that all my current responsibilities and assigned tasks are completed in advance to avoid any disruption in workflow.\nKindly consider my request and grant approval for the mentioned dates.\n\nThank you for your understanding.\n\nRegards,\nYashpal Singh\nSEO Executive', 'approved', 2, '2026-05-25 08:36:31', '2026-05-25 11:52:54'),
