(62, 26, 'Full Day', 'Paid Leave', '2026-05-30', '2026-05-30', NULL, NULL, 'I will be out of the station', 'Dear Sir/Ma\'am,\n\nI would like to request leave for 30th May (Saturday), as I will be out of the station and will not be able to attend the office on that day.\n\nPlease consider my leave request and let me know if any further information is required.\n\nThank you for your understanding.\n\nRegards,\nGourav Mehta', 'approved', 1, '2026-05-27 04:54:32', '2026-05-29 12:57:06'),
