(68, 116, NULL, '<div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"1\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• TODAYS DEADLINE OPEN MODEL</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">1h</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"1hye1uz\" data-start=\"29\" data-end=\"107\">Added <strong data-start=\"37\" data-end=\"69\">Today’s Deadline popup/model</strong> to show orders with today’s deadline.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1i7cxf7\" data-start=\"109\" data-end=\"213\">\r\nRestricted the popup visibility to allowed roles only: <strong data-start=\"166\" data-end=\"212\">Super Admin, Marketing Team, and Sub Admin</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1py5l2m\" data-start=\"215\" data-end=\"280\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nDisplayed deadline order details in the model for quick review.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"2.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• ADD BREAK BTN</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">2h 30m</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"1ijhk2l\" data-start=\"29\" data-end=\"86\">Added a <strong data-start=\"39\" data-end=\"55\">Break button</strong> before the working time timer.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1kzpfd3\" data-start=\"88\" data-end=\"173\">\r\nAdded <strong data-start=\"96\" data-end=\"111\">Lunch Break</strong> and <strong data-start=\"116\" data-end=\"129\">Tea Break</strong> options with start/end break functionality.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"jvrphs\" data-start=\"175\" data-end=\"289\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nSaved break details in DB, including employee, break type, start time, end time, total break duration, and date.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"1\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• ADD HISTORY IN ORDER WORD AND PRICE </strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">1h</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"1f4rff4\" data-start=\"29\" data-end=\"96\">Added <strong data-start=\"37\" data-end=\"60\">history popup/model</strong> for order <strong data-start=\"71\" data-end=\"95\">word count and price</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1ib9ap4\" data-start=\"98\" data-end=\"208\">\r\nDisplayed all additional word count and additional price entries with <strong data-start=\"170\" data-end=\"189\">created by user</strong> and <strong data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"207\">date/time</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1czf7y7\" data-start=\"210\" data-end=\"338\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nUpdated order list to show values like <strong data-start=\"251\" data-end=\"267\">100+10 words</strong> and <strong data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"290\">£100+£10 price</strong> without changing the original base value in DB.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"0.75\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• ADD COMMENT BOX IN LEAD</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">45m</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"yi6nqf\" data-start=\"29\" data-end=\"79\">Added a <strong data-start=\"39\" data-end=\"54\">Comment Box</strong> column in the Lead list.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"6xfwg\" data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"142\">\r\nDisplayed the latest lead comment from the <strong data-start=\"126\" data-end=\"141\">calls table</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1wl92i\" data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"221\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nShowed comment details with user name, comment text, and created date/time</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"1\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• ADD FILTER IN REFUNG MODULE</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">1h</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"w6g2j3\" data-start=\"29\" data-end=\"136\">Added filters in the <strong data-start=\"52\" data-end=\"81\">Looking For Refund Orders</strong> module for <strong data-start=\"93\" data-end=\"135\">Order ID, User, Status, and Date Range</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"185yi0f\" data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"202\">\r\nImplemented user search by <strong data-start=\"167\" data-end=\"201\">name, email, and mobile number</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"sbjcsf\" data-start=\"204\" data-end=\"295\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nUpdated the report listing to show filtered refund orders based on the selected criteria.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"0.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• PRIME ASSIGNMENT OR SMART ASSIGNMENT LEADS ISSUE</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">30m</b></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"182e3t4\" data-start=\"44\" data-end=\"146\">Added routes and controller method for the <strong data-start=\"89\" data-end=\"138\">New Users, Retain Users, and Not Retain Users</strong> report.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"vwsya1\" data-start=\"148\" data-end=\"220\">\r\nImplemented the logic to fetch users based on their latest order date.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"6ab9ia\" data-start=\"222\" data-end=\"293\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nTested the report API/route in <strong data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"266\">Postman</strong> and verified the response.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"1.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• NEW USER, RETAIN OR NOT RETAIN    </strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">1h 30m</b><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 116, 139); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\"><li data-section-id=\"1mipmrw\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"117\">Added a <strong data-start=\"10\" data-end=\"35\">User Retention Report</strong> with three categories: <strong data-start=\"59\" data-end=\"72\">New Users</strong>, <strong data-start=\"74\" data-end=\"90\">Retain Users</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"96\" data-end=\"116\">Not Retain Users</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"jk1t44\" data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"194\">\r\n<strong data-start=\"121\" data-end=\"134\" data-is-only-node=\"\">New Users</strong> shows users whose latest order is in the <strong data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"193\">current month</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1qb651w\" data-start=\"196\" data-end=\"308\">\r\n<strong data-start=\"198\" data-end=\"214\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Retain Users</strong> shows users whose latest order was in the <strong data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"278\">previous 2 months</strong>, excluding the current month.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"13rakzr\" data-start=\"310\" data-end=\"403\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<strong data-start=\"312\" data-end=\"332\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Not Retain Users</strong> shows users who have not placed any order for the last <strong data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"402\">8–9 months</strong>.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">', 'Rahul Sharma', '8.25', NULL, '2026-05-22 12:41:25', '2026-05-22 12:41:25'),
