e992\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden\"><div class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling\"><ol data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"570\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><li data-section-id=\"1eof6h4\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"138\">Completed the dynamic functionality for all Country Pages with proper data loading and smooth content rendering across all countries.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1cg1b2d\" data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"265\">\r\nFixed country-wise dynamic structure issues by improving page mapping, content display flow, and navigation performance.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"tdxx44\" data-start=\"267\" data-end=\"404\">\r\nOptimized dynamic country sections with responsive layouts, proper UI alignment, and consistent design support for all screen sizes.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"a2m4n7\" data-start=\"406\" data-end=\"570\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nCompleted the dynamic implementation for the Country Pages, while the Hero Section and Sub Hero Section enhancements are currently remaining for further updates.</li></ol></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">', 'Ranjit Singh Shaktawat', '2.50', NULL, '2026-05-25 11:21:29', '2026-05-25 11:21:29'),
(111, 196, NULL, '<li data-section-id=\"3x4mol\" data-start=\"137\" data-end=\"259\">Fixed data accuracy issues in <strong data-start=\"170\" data-end=\"184\">Categories</strong> and <strong data-start=\"189\" data-end=\"206\">Subcategories</strong> pages, including product count and status display.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"cpmxie\" data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"376\">\r\nImproved <strong data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"315\">pagination, search, and filter handling</strong> for Customers, Suppliers, Transporters, and listing pages.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"dyr6gi\" data-start=\"377\" data-end=\"500\">\r\nFixed UI and action issues in <strong data-start=\"410\" data-end=\"491\">Suppliers, Transporters, Business Profile, Sale Details, and Purchase Details</strong> pages.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"wsvlgd\" data-start=\"501\" data-end=\"620\">\r\nImproved validation for <strong data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"611\">Expenses, Shifts, Opening Stock, Barcode Labels, Business Profile, and Settings</strong> pages.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1izyfy9\" data-start=\"621\" data-end=\"732\">\r\nFixed functional gaps in <strong data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"720\">Import Items, Barcode Generator, Activity Logs, and Change Password</strong> sections.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"e01dnp\" data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"834\">\r\nImproved <strong data-start=\"745\" data-end=\"768\">Opening Stock Entry</strong> logic to avoid duplicate stock and incorrect price/tax updates.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"7j6ws4\" data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"936\">\r\nUpdated <strong data-start=\"846\" data-end=\"913\">payment, cash/bank, cheque transaction, and stock-related flows</strong> for better accuracy.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"6048l8\" data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"1056\">\r\nCleaned UI consistency issues across pages, including icons, avatars, buttons, tables, and mobile/touch usability.</li>', 'Mangilal Gadri', '0.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 11:22:28', '2026-05-25 11:22:28'),
(112, 195, NULL, '<li data-section-id=\"16cw9mh\" data-start=\"110\" data-end=\"183\">Updated the <strong data-start=\"125\" data-end=\"145\">POS Billing page</strong> UI for a cleaner and better layout.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"xa3emh\" data-start=\"184\" data-end=\"271\">\r\nFixed the <strong data-start=\"197\" data-end=\"237\">right-side panel, table, and top bar</strong> design on the POS Billing page.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"i9yi6x\" data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"346\">\r\nFixed the <strong data-start=\"285\" data-end=\"299\">global CSS</strong> to maintain the same style across all pages.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1knj451\" data-start=\"347\" data-end=\"449\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\nStandardized <strong data-start=\"363\" data-end=\"416\">colors, buttons, headings, subheadings, and fonts</strong> across all pages and components.</li>', 'Mangilal Gadri', '0.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 11:24:35', '2026-05-25 11:24:35'),
