(119, 20, NULL, '<h3 data-section-id=\"imr561\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"34\"><span role=\"text\"><strong data-start=\"4\" data-end=\"34\">Task Report — May 25, 2026</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"36\" data-end=\"201\">• Performed complete testing of <strong data-start=\"68\" data-end=\"89\">Mewar ERP Chatbot</strong><br data-start=\"89\" data-end=\"92\">\r\n○ Tested all query scenarios and chatbot workflows<br data-start=\"142\" data-end=\"145\">\r\n○ Verified response accuracy and overall functionality</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"203\" data-end=\"359\">• Solved possible system and logic errors<br data-start=\"244\" data-end=\"247\">\r\n○ Fixed bugs affecting chatbot performance and response handling<br data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"314\">\r\n○ Improved system stability and reliability</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"361\" data-end=\"493\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">• Deployed <strong data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"393\">Mewar ERP Chatbot</strong> on <strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"413\">Hugging Face</strong><br data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"416\">\r\n○ Configured deployment setup and validated functionality after deployment</p>', 'love kumar todawat', '0.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:40:12', '2026-05-25 12:40:12'),
(120, 210, NULL, '<div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"2\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• MEETING REGARDING TMS</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">2h</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">', 'ANSHUL SUTHAR (KHETA RAM)', '2.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:40:46', '2026-05-25 12:40:46'),
(121, 212, NULL, '<div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"8.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• PROJECT WORK FLOW</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">8h 30m</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">implemented the dynamic project progress recalculation in the Project module, where progress updates automatically based on changes in main stages and sub stages. I also added the Project Workflow feature with two modes: Sequential Flow and Free Flow, and stored the flow type in the database for each project. The flow selection is now integrated into the system and reflects correctly in the project view. Additionally, the logic structure for handling flow-based progress calculation has been completed and integrated with existing project data.', 'Manish patidar', '8.50', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:43:22', '2026-05-25 12:43:22'),
(122, 193, NULL, '<div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"0.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• SYSTEM ISSUE</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">30m</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li>&nbsp;System went to recovery mode, and fails to restart.</li><li>Waited to fix the issue.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"1.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• COPY ALL THE MODELS, CONTROLLER, VIEW</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">1h 30m</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li>&nbsp;Copied all the relations of hrms into saas-erp.</li><li>Solve the errors such as edit, create is not working, view file is not loading, database issue.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"0.5\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• SETUP HRMS PROJECT LOCALLY</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">30m</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li>&nbsp;Setup the project, and analyze Database to integrate it in saas-erp.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">', 'Jay Sahu', '2.50', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:45:40', '2026-05-25 12:45:40'),
(123, 211, NULL, '<p><div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"6\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• MFU APIS</strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">6h</b></p><h3 data-section-id=\"xivw4z\" data-start=\"65\" data-end=\"93\">1. CAN &amp; Mandate Testing</h3></div></p><ul data-start=\"94\" data-end=\"247\">\r\n<li data-section-id=\"17dhfi3\" data-start=\"94\" data-end=\"121\">\r\nTest CAN Registration API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"15nmes\" data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"149\">\r\nTest CAN Modification API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"q01nx1\" data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"181\">\r\nTest UPI Mandate Creation API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1p6li7s\" data-start=\"182\" data-end=\"215\">\r\nTest eNACH Mandate Creation API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"602qjm\" data-start=\"216\" data-end=\"247\">\r\nTest Mandate Status Check API\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><h3 data-section-id=\"11ckqgr\" data-start=\"249\" data-end=\"283\">2. Mandate Auto Debit Push API</h3><ul data-start=\"284\" data-end=\"473\">\r\n<li data-section-id=\"kmpdzn\" data-start=\"284\" data-end=\"340\">\r\nCreate push API to receive mandate auto-debit response\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1r6870f\" data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"373\">\r\nStore debit status in database\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1nah8ml\" data-start=\"374\" data-end=\"417\">\r\nHandle success, failed, pending responses\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"c0vdli\" data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"473\">\r\nMap response with user, CAN, mandate reference number\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><h3 data-section-id=\"5s8tt9\" data-start=\"475\" data-end=\"509\">3. Transaction Status Push API</h3><ul data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"734\">\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1kahkf1\" data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"562\">\r\nCreate push API for MFU transaction status updates\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"t5mrjb\" data-start=\"563\" data-end=\"620\">\r\nStore order status, payment status and rejection reason\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1ubedsn\" data-start=\"621\" data-end=\"693\">\r\nMap status using <code data-start=\"640\" data-end=\"649\">mfuGorn</code>, <code data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"657\">corn</code>, <code data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"665\">itrn</code>, or unique reference number\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1y9o9y\" data-start=\"694\" data-end=\"734\">\r\nUpdate transaction table automatically\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><h3 data-section-id=\"p5ii2x\" data-start=\"736\" data-end=\"770\">4. Systematic Transaction APIs</h3><ul data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"947\">\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1dwgzw0\" data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"793\">\r\nCreate SIP Order API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"v3qw32\" data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"816\">\r\nCreate SWP Order API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"f8k39h\" data-start=\"817\" data-end=\"847\">\r\nCreate Step-up SIP logic/API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"nf5zw7\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"897\">\r\nSave systematic transaction details in database\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1uxydej\" data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"947\">\r\nSupport UPI AutoPay and eNACH mandate reference\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><h3 data-section-id=\"1mbaau9\" data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"973\">5. Cancellation APIs</h3><p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><ul data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1144\">\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1n668do\" data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1016\">\r\nCreate Systematic Transaction Cancel API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"811lc5\" data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1055\">\r\nCreate Normal Transaction Cancel API\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1ot7zll\" data-start=\"1056\" data-end=\"1097\">\r\nStore cancellation request and response\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1tzrbiy\" data-start=\"1098\" data-end=\"1144\">\r\nUpdate transaction status after cancellation</li></ul><p><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\"></p>', 'ANSHUL SUTHAR (KHETA RAM)', '6.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:46:04', '2026-05-25 12:46:04'),
(124, 194, NULL, '<div class=\"sub-task-item mb-4\" data-time=\"8\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid #3858f9; padding-left: 20px;\">\r\n                                                            <p class=\"mb-2\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b;\"><strong>• CHANGES IN DAILY TASK MODULE AND IMPLEMENT JOB REQUIREMENT AND EMPLOYEE REVIEW MODULE </strong> — <b style=\"color: #3858f9;\">8h</b></p>\r\n                                                            <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;\">\r\n                                                                <li data-section-id=\"u8e5be\" data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"211\">Improved <strong data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"134\">Task Details</strong> and <strong data-start=\"139\" data-end=\"156\">Work Progress</strong> section UI for better readability and user experience.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1x5sio8\" data-start=\"212\" data-end=\"296\">\r\nRedesigned task information layout for a cleaner and more structured presentation.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1vadssh\" data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"390\">\r\nImplemented new <strong data-start=\"315\" data-end=\"341\">Job Requirement Module</strong> with complete form structure and workflow setup.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"zayjzh\" data-start=\"391\" data-end=\"483\">\r\nAdded candidate type selection with dynamic <strong data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"468\">Experience field visibility</strong> functionality.</li><li data-section-id=\"iypvq3\" data-start=\"876\" data-end=\"939\">Started implementation of the new <strong data-start=\"912\" data-end=\"938\">Employee Review Module</strong>.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"we8h5a\" data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"1003\">\r\nCreated initial Employee Review form structure and UI layout.\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-section-id=\"1vulod9\" data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1060\">\r\nImplemented basic review fields and module flow setup.</li><li data-section-id=\"1vulod9\" data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1060\">Ongoing development for employee performance review process and reporting features.</li>\r\n                                                            </ol>\r\n                                                          </div><hr class=\"sub-task-hr\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 20px 0;\">', 'Mohammad Kaif', '8.00', NULL, '2026-05-25 12:49:12', '2026-05-25 12:49:12'),
