(184, 273, 15, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; WTS Frontend</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 8h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">WTS Visa:</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Developed the complete UI for the new Blog Page based on the provided Figma design and structured it into reusable components.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Implemented full mobile responsiveness and optimized layouts for different screen sizes.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Created and integrated a new Countries Page form.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Designed the Services Page UI and worked on its frontend structure.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Made minor improvements including:</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Updated the WhatsApp chat integration message</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Managed and optimized page spacing and layout alignment</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">SIP Project:</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Reviewed and tested the overall SIP page functionality during the initial phase of the day.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Nikhil Sharma', '8', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:21:52', '2026-05-27 12:21:52'),
(185, 266, 15, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; WTS Frontend</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 8h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Fixed and optimized dynamic functionality for multiple sections on the Country Pages to ensure accurate data rendering and smooth content updates across all country-wise pages.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Resolved section-wise dynamic issues by properly integrating APIs/database content, improving page performance, and maintaining consistent layout behavior on different screen sizes.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Recovered previously removed Home Page and Country Page code that was accidentally deleted automatically, restored the old structure, and re-implemented the required fixes and dynamic functionality.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Updated and refined several Country Page sections with improved UI structure, proper dynamic content handling, and better responsiveness for a smoother user experience.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Home Page desktop structure and major UI fixes have been completed, while mobile responsiveness and a few responsive adjustments are still pending for final optimization.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Ranjit Singh Shaktawat', '8', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:22:11', '2026-05-27 12:22:11'),
(186, 275, 20, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Mewar HighTech (ERP)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 7h 30m</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Created complete Project Documents module with database table, model, routes and controller logic.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Implemented document upload, view, download and delete functionality using Laravel storage system.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Added dynamic documents listing from database on project detail page.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Improved Project Overview UI with scrollable documents and comments section.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Worked on workflow warning modal and optimized workflow/stage handling logic.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Manish patidar', '7.5', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:25:22', '2026-05-27 12:25:22'),
