(216, 291, 15, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; WTS Frontend</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 8h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">WTS Visa:</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Developed and integrated the new Blog Page with dynamic content functionality.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Redirected the old blog page to the newly developed blog page.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Improved and optimized the Country Page responsiveness across mobile and tablet devices.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Updated the Landing Page Registration UI for a better user experience.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Reworked the Multi-Step Form according to the provided reference form and enhanced its overall UI.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Completely redesigned and updated the EMI Calculator Page UI based on the new design requirements.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Continued development of the EMI Calculator module, with approximately 50% of the functionality and UI implementation completed.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Worked on calculator page layouts, styling, responsiveness, and user experience improvements.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Nikhil Sharma', '8', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:25:41', '2026-05-29 12:25:41'),
(217, 300, 31, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; PITHAL MACHINES LTD. Graphics</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 7h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Pithal website pending pages UI design, the whole 3 pages design, and share with Mangilal, and generate some images (14) for product page UI design, review mobile view for home page, and give suggestions in the UI</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Gourav Mehta', '7', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:26:08', '2026-05-29 12:26:08'),
(218, 302, 51, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; SIP Mobile App</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 8h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Goal save functionality integrated with SIP and Lumpsum API.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">After saving the goal, a future date selection UI was created for SIP goals.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">&quot;Invest Now&quot; option added in Compare Fund section.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">&quot;Explore Fund&quot; option added in all 3 Home Page calculators.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Harsha Kalal', '8', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:32:18', '2026-05-29 12:32:18'),
(219, 298, 15, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; WTS Frontend</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 8h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Redesigned the complete Home Page with a modern and clean UI structure for a better user experience. Improved overall section alignment, layout flow, and visual presentation across the page.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Implemented full responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices. Fixed spacing, section responsiveness, and screen-wise layout adjustments.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Refined and fixed multiple Home Page animations for smoother interaction and better visual consistency. Optimized animation behavior and properly adjusted section transitions.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Reworked the Home Page structure and fixed several UI alignment issues across different sections. Improved overall page consistency, responsiveness, and performance.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Worked on Country Pages and made Hero Section background images fully dynamic. Integrated dynamic image handling for proper country-wise content display.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Fixed font sizes, text alignment, and updated multiple text sections on Country Pages. Improved UI consistency, responsiveness, and readability across all country-wise pages.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Ranjit Singh Shaktawat', '8', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:35:31', '2026-05-29 12:35:31'),
(220, 299, 27, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; WTS Graphics</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 1h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">working on it</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Gourav Mehta', '1', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:35:52', '2026-05-29 12:35:52');
INSERT INTO `task_follow_ups` (`id`, `daily_task_id`, `project_id`, `work_description`, `reference_name`, `time_taken`, `photo`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(221, 296, 53, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Other (Development)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 0h 30m</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Setup Backend Bharat Ceramics project and saw product excel sheet to import.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Created a pendrive bootable to install windows 10 in other system using rufus.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Jay Sahu', '0.5', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:48:17', '2026-05-29 12:48:17'),
(222, 303, 6, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; AIN Portal</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 5h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Reviewed and adjusted Payments List sorting logic to prioritize records based on account status while maintaining latest-date ordering.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Tested and verified report calculations and data visibility across different user categories</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Cloned the backend on the server and fixed the bugs</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Rahul Sharma', '5', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:53:38', '2026-05-29 12:53:38'),
(223, 303, 53, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Other (Development)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 1h 40m</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Checked and fixed the excessive additional CSS applied to the Prime Assignment section, which was affecting the blog UI</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Rahul Sharma', '1.6666666666667', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:53:38', '2026-05-29 12:53:38'),
(224, 303, 53, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Other (Development)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 1h 30m</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Set up the Pithal Machines project locally, discussed it with Mangilal, and also discussed Ain’s changes.</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'Rahul Sharma', '1.5', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:53:38', '2026-05-29 12:53:38'),
(225, 293, 9, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Iron street ( SMM)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 0h 30m</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Post story</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">check if scheduled post posted on all platforms</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'fatema', '0.5', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:53:42', '2026-05-29 12:53:42'),
(226, 305, 2, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; SIP Backend</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 6h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">SIP BACKEND CREATE GOAL FLOW API</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">CREATE PORTFOLIO API</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">TEST API AND DEPLOY</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'ANSHUL SUTHAR (KHETA RAM)', '6', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:57:00', '2026-05-29 12:57:00'),
(227, 305, 53, '\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"padding-left: 8px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;\">\n                <p class=\"mb-3\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                    <span style=\"color: #1e293b;\">&bull; Other (Development)</span>\n                    <span style=\"color: #3858f9; font-weight: 700;\"> - 3h</span>\n                </p>\n                <ol class=\"text-muted\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 24px; color: #64748b; margin: 0;\">\n                    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">MEETING</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">PROBLEM SOLVE</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>', 'ANSHUL SUTHAR (KHETA RAM)', '3', NULL, '2026-05-29 12:57:00', '2026-05-29 12:57:00'),
